snippet.title: "It's Over" Johnny Depp Speaks On New Amber Heard Documentary
snippet.description:
Johnny Depp Finally Speaks On The New Documentary About Him And Amber Heard!

✅ Subscribe & HIT that notification bell for more Celebrity Content!

The bitter split between Johnny Depp and Amber Heard became one of the most high-profile divorce dramas in recent memory. New details are revealed in the new documentary Johnny vs Amber. On Nov. 19, Discovery+ announced an upcoming documentary about Johnny Depp and Amber Heard's 2017 divorce, which is still being debated in the public eye. But what would this mean to the case and the trial? Let’s talk about it!

#JohnnyDepp #AmberHeard
